#### `onListPostClick()`
A click handler added to all list-post elements by `initListPosts()`. Adds the 
'.ldc-focus' class to the clicked list-post, and removes it from all others. 

      onListPostClick: ->
        $('.ldc-list-wrap .ldc-list-post').removeClass 'ldc-focus'
        $(@).addClass 'ldc-focus'




